{"tid":2224952,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【武漢肺炎】英國 7,143宗新確診 創單日確診紀錄，法國全歐最多人病死","createTime":"2020-10-01T03:02:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-04T10:11:57.000Z","uid":79563,"like":14,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"aaabb5daaf7e65e3a6c4279a6f9f9fc3015edf79","tid":2224952,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T03:02:16.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/international/武漢肺炎-英國荷蘭創單日確診記錄-法全歐最多人病死/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Finternational%2F%E6%AD%A6%E6%BC%A2%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E-%E8%8B%B1%E5%9C%8B%E8%8D%B7%E8%98%AD%E5%89%B5%E5%96%AE%E6%97%A5%E7%A2%BA%E8%A8%BA%E8%A8%98%E9%8C%84-%E6%B3%95%E5%85%A8%E6%AD%90%E6%9C%80%E5%A4%9A%E4%BA%BA%E7%97%85%E6%AD%BB%2F&d=zLqexyjt4FDe6khRmo8kykkSG0DzaVerHR9pE4rwCb4%3D&h=b9db2c7a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Finternational%2F%E6%AD%A6%E6%BC%A2%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E-%E8%8B%B1%E5%9C%8B%E8%8D%B7%E8%98%AD%E5%89%B5%E5%96%AE%E6%97%A5%E7%A2%BA%E8%A8%BA%E8%A8%98%E9%8C%84-%E6%B3%95%E5%85%A8%E6%AD%90%E6%9C%80%E5%A4%9A%E4%BA%BA%E7%97%85%E6%AD%BB%2F&h=115fe29f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/international/武漢肺炎-英國荷蘭創單日確診記錄-法全歐最多人病死/</a><br />\n<br />\n歐洲第二波武漢肺炎 (COVID-19) 疫情嚴峻。英國截至當地周二 (29/9) 早上 9 時，單日新增 7,143 宗實驗室確診感染 COVID-19 個案，創下疫情至今的最大單日新增確診紀錄，而現時該國已累積超過 44.6 萬人感染 COVID-19 。<br />\n<br />\n英國政府亦公佈再有 71 人於病毒測試呈陽性後 28 日內病死，令全國累積病死人數達 42,072 。不過，英國多個統計機構發表的獨立數據顯示，目前在該國死亡證上有登記 COVID-19 為死因的人接近 57,900 位。<br />\n<br />\n隨著感染人數再暴增，英國市民的活動都受到進一步的限制，包括英格蘭擴大口罩令以及蘇格蘭的家庭聚會禁令等。<br />\n<br />\n荷蘭同樣創單日感染紀錄<br />\n<br />\n荷蘭同樣在周二破紀錄地單日錄得 3,011 宗確診感染個案，當局指全國幾乎所有地區與所有年齡層都有顯著感染個案上升。早前該國已宣佈周二晚起食肆須在未來 3 星期晚上 10 時前關門，亦要求所有運動賽事閉門作賽。<br />\n<br />\n法國全歐最多人病死<br />\n<br />\n法國累積 31,908 宗 COVID-19 病死個案，是全歐最多。在馬賽和附近的普羅旺斯地區艾克斯，酒吧和餐館被要求關閉以阻止病毒傳播，措施將持續至少兩周。但法國中央政府無視巴黎的感染和住院人數正在上升，下令對包括巴黎在內的其他十個城市實行更寬鬆的限制措施。"},{"pid":"d0ee43b3725516b1e33ad466b08bb9023d3ecc22","tid":2224952,"uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T03:02:37.000Z","msg":"英國係咪已經放棄狀態？"},{"pid":"18494d095b1698c3131aea1e48639aca99ee63ff","tid":2224952,"uid":98117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T03:02:58.000Z","msg":"如果你已經唔記得當初喺為咩而行出嚟，當初喺為咩而憤怒，就入嚟睇下條片<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n【自由之歌】有個香港人無收錢整咗條咁嘅片出嚟<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2224648\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2224648</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"3d34030a2b0563f40daf37cc438385e1ed1752d0","tid":2224952,"uid":155095,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T03:05:11.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"red\">中國成最大贏家 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n習近平永垂不朽</span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static02-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2620000/2620233/chung_thumb_20200417_ch_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic02-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2620000%2F2620233%2Fchung_thumb_20200417_ch_1024.jpg&h=03f22169&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://assets.post852.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/11190623/004.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fassets.post852.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F03%2F11190623%2F004.jpg&h=bf3d80aa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static01-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2575000/2577170/sme_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic01-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2575000%2F2577170%2Fsme_1024.jpg&h=72c0e1ed&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"92ed8fb5859785da39482556ec6cae88a327b75c","tid":2224952,"uid":169801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T03:07:29.000Z","msg":"法國死人仲可以多過意大利<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5